ied-for-stamping-star-of-david-on-palestinians-face/0000018f-c41d-d0b7-abdf-ccbfd4d30000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵在拉法爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</link><description>这些士兵是参谋军士。阿米尔·加利洛夫，20 岁，参谋军士。乌里·巴尔·奥尔（Uri Bar Or）和参谋中士。伊多·阿佩尔，21 岁</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙承认巴勒斯坦，内塔尼亚胡在以色列欢迎西班牙反伊斯兰党领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</link><description>西班牙极右翼 Vox 党领袖圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡 (Santiago Abascal) 因伊斯兰恐惧症、反移民言论和反 LGBTQ 立场而受到批评，他来到以色列会见内塔尼亚胡，谴责西班牙左翼政府</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</guid></item><item><title>汉娜·阿伦特将如何回应以色列被指控犯有反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</link><description>阿伦特逃离了纳粹，并因报道艾希曼审判而闻名，他坚信国际刑事法院可以防止种族灭绝。那么她会支持国际刑事法院对以色列和哈马斯领导人发出的潜在逮捕令吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:58:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</guid></item><item><title>妮基·黑利在以色列军队炮弹上涂写暴力信息，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</link><description>在参观10月7日以色列南部遭到袭击的地点时，失败的共和党总统候选人加入了签署以色列国防军导弹的潮流。 “你能带她回去吗？”一位和平活动人士反驳道，“我们已经有了一个本-格维尔”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人向以色列城镇开枪 以色列国防军称无人伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-shoot-at-israeli-town-idf-says-no-casualties/0000018f-c3cd-d822-a58f-d7dd35bb0000</link><description>埃梅克·赫弗地区委员会主席表示，这起事件并不罕见，该地区的枪击事件“已经成为每天”发生的事情，居民证明他们生活在恐惧之中</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-shoot-at-israeli-town-idf-says-no-casualties/0000018f-c3cd-d822-a58f-d7dd35bb0000</guid></item><item><title>Robo-Zelda：以色列军队的无人装甲运兵车在拉法被发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/robo-zelda-israeli-armys-remote-controlled-apc-robots-spotted-in-gazas-rafah/0000018f-c38d-dade-adef-efaf644d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦当地人在社交媒体上发布了在拉法运行的机器人的视频片段，他们称它们为“诱杀坦克”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/robo-zelda-israeli-armys-remote-controlled-apc-robots-spotted-in-gazas-rafah/0000018f-c38d-dade-adef-efaf644d0000</guid></item><item><title>遍体鳞伤：以色列反战抗议者受伤被送上法庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/bruised-and-battered-israeli-anti-war-protesters-brought-to-court-with-injuries/0000018f-c32d-d822-a58f-d73db8840000</link><description>在法庭延长拘留听证会上，其中一名妇女的手臂上有石膏，另一名妇女的脖子上有瘀伤的迹象。她的律师说，其中一名抗议者“在逮捕过程中被按在地上并被窒息”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/bruised-and-battered-israeli-anti-war-protesters-brought-to-court-with-injuries/0000018f-c32d-d822-a58f-d73db8840000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列团体帮助共和党议员击败拿大屠杀开玩笑的极右翼共和党人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-groups-help-defeat-far-right-republican-who-joked-about-holocaust/0000018f-c25a-d822-a58f-d75e37e10000</link><description>AIPAC 附属超级政治行动委员会和共和党犹太联盟的参与是 2024 年选举周期中最重要的参与之一</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 06:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-groups-help-defeat-far-right-republican-who-joked-about-holocaust/0000018f-c25a-d822-a58f-d75e37e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的致命疏忽威胁到美国对拉法行动的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/after-israels-callous-carelessness-in-rafah-washington-now-calls-the-shots/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafea9a80000</link><description>本周加沙发生的两起大规模人员伤亡事件表明，国际社会不再愿意听取以色列的解释，对以色列国防军也不再像七个月前那样耐心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 03:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/after-israels-callous-carelessness-in-rafah-washington-now-calls-the-shots/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafea9a80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡灾难性的政府团结起来生存，但以色列反对派仍然分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-government-has-united-to-survive-but-the-opposition-remains-divided/0000018f-c111-d822-a58f-d51ddf4d0000</link><description>生存本能和对权力的渴望迫使以色列执政联盟的成员紧密团结在一起，而反对派甚至无法就谁将领导反内塔尼亚胡集团达成一致——该集团得到了大多数以色列人的支持，并且有能力推翻以色列政府。政府</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 03:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-government-has-united-to-survive-but-the-opposition-remains-divided/0000018f-c111-d822-a58f-d51ddf4d0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：以色列必须推进加沙计划，美国期待对“可怕的”拉法袭击事件进行调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-live/algerian-draft-un-resolution-calls-for-immediate-gaza-truce-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018f-c21e-d822-a58f-d71ef94a0000</link><description>以色列国家安全顾问称加沙战斗将持续到2024年 ■ 土耳其埃尔多安称内塔尼亚胡为“以血为食的吸血鬼” ■ 哈马斯声称对以色列中部城镇的枪击事件负责 ■ 报告：以色列对拉法的致命袭击中使用了美国弹药 ■ 以色列飞机击落地中海上空可疑空中目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:17:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-live/algerian-draft-un-resolution-calls-for-immediate-gaza-truce-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018f-c21e-d822-a58f-d71ef94a0000</guid></item><item><title>“不再是禁忌”：欧盟高级外交官告诉《国土报》，更多欧洲国家考虑承认巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/more-european-states-considering-recognizing-palestine-senior-eu-diplomat-tells-haaretz/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafeb4cd0000</link><description>布鲁塞尔中东和平进程特别代表表示，其他成员国可能会效仿西班牙、挪威和爱尔兰</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 21:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/more-european-states-considering-recognizing-palestine-senior-eu-diplomat-tells-haaretz/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafeb4cd0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在加沙部署的武器可以帮助以色列对抗真主党的无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/what-the-u-s-stationed-at-the-gaza-coast-could-help-israel-against-hezbollahs-drones/0000018f-bf87-d19e-a19f-ffe77df70000</link><description>以色列留下短程高射炮二十年后，真主党正在利用无人机来利用防空系统的漏洞，增加了这些武器重返前线的可能性</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 20:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/what-the-u-s-stationed-at-the-gaza-coast-could-help-israel-against-hezbollahs-drones/0000018f-bf87-d19e-a19f-ffe77df70000</guid></item><item><title>拉比德尔菲娜·霍维勒 (Delphine Horvilleur)：“犹太复国主义关乎力量。 10 月 7 日之后，以色列人理解了破碎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-28/ty-article-podcast/zionisms-narrative-is-about-strength-after-oct-7-israelis-understand-brokenness/0000018f-c01b-d053-a1bf-ec1f063f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-28/ty-article-podcast/zionisms-narrative-is-about-strength-after-oct-7-israelis-understand-brokenness/0000018f-c01b-d053-a1bf-ec1f063f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列否认对拉法附近营地的袭击，加沙官员称袭击造成 21 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-officials-21-dead-in-new-israeli-attack-on-tent-camp-in-west-rafah/0000018f-bfc0-dfeb-a58f-bffa1c4f0000</link><description>据卫生部称，共有64人受伤，其中10人伤势严重。市政府官员表示，袭击发生在以色列国防军指定为安全区的地区</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:22:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-officials-21-dead-in-new-israeli-attack-on-tent-camp-in-west-rafah/0000018f-bfc0-dfeb-a58f-bffa1c4f0000</guid></item><item><title>《卫报》：以色列多年来一直在监视国际刑事法院首席检察官，包括最近几个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-guardian-israel-spied-for-years-on-icc-chief-prosecutor-including-in-recent-months/0000018f-bfe0-dfeb-a58f-bffa942f0000</link><description>《卫报》、Local Call 和 +972 的调查揭露了以色列涉嫌针对国际刑事法院及其官员的秘密行动。内塔尼亚胡被描述为“痴迷于”针对他的案件，而据报道，前摩萨德主席约西·科恩在秘密会议上威胁前首席检察官</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-guardian-israel-spied-for-years-on-icc-chief-prosecutor-including-in-recent-months/0000018f-bfe0-dfeb-a58f-bffa942f0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军将军亚伊尔·戈兰横扫工党选举，誓言团结以色列分裂的左翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-general-yair-golan-clinches-labor-party-election-vows-to-rally-israels-fractured-left/0000018f-c047-dade-adef-ecefdf300000</link><description>戈兰以 95% 的选票获胜，工党议员支持他的竞选，旨在团结以色列犹太复国主义左翼。他在胜选演说中表示，我们将全力以赴推翻政府并推进选举</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-general-yair-golan-clinches-labor-party-election-vows-to-rally-israels-fractured-left/0000018f-c047-dade-adef-ecefdf300000</guid></item></channel></rss>